i-corner-bottom,.ui-corner-right,.ui-corner-br{border-bottom-right-radius:4px}.ui-widget-overlay{background:#666 url(images/ui-bg_diagonals-thick_20_666666_40x40.png) 50% 50% repeat;opacity:.5;filter:Alpha(Opacity=50)}.ui-widget-shadow{margin:-5px 0 0 -5px;padding:5px;background:#000 url(images/ui-bg_flat_10_000000_40x100.png) 50% 50% repeat-x;opacity:.2;filter:Alpha(Opacity=20);border-radius:5px}.link-web>a{color:#555;font-size:12px;line-height:24px}body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m qua 26/4, ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch ki\u00eam TG\u0110 VPF, \u00f4ng Tr\u1ea7n Anh T\u00fa \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 r\u00fat kh\u1ecfi danh s\u00e1ch \u1ee9ng c\u1eed v\u00e0o ch\u1ee9c Ph\u00f3 Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh v\u00e0 v\u1eadn \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u00e0i tr\u1ee3 VFF kh\u00f3a VIII.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 t\u1eeb b\u1ea7u \u0110\u1ee9c, ng\u01b0\u1eddi tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 h\u00f9ng h\u1ed3n tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 s\u1ebd cho HAGL ngh\u1ec9 V-League n\u1ebfu b\u1ea7u T\u00fa c\u00f3 gh\u1ebf trong VFF.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV HAGL Duong Minh Ninh\" title=\"HLV HAGL D\u01b0\u01a1ng Minh Ninh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/14/hlv-duong-minh-ninh-noi-gi-sau-khi-bau-tu-khong-tranh-cu-vff.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HLV HAGL D\u01b0\u01a1ng Minh Ninh kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh vi\u1ec7c b\u1ea7u T\u00fa kh\u00f4ng tranh c\u1eed l\u00e0 tin vui v\u1edbi&nbsp;HAGL</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong cu\u1ed9c trao \u0111\u1ed5i c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u1edbi b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi trong n\u01b0\u1edbc, \u00f4ng ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai c\u0169ng l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng cho bi\u1ebft:&nbsp; &ldquo;Quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a anh T\u00fa r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t, r\u1ea5t c\u00f3 l\u1ee3i cho b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam. Anh T\u00fa t\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3 c\u0169ng s\u1ebd c\u00f3 th\u1eddi gian ch\u0103m s\u00f3c cho VPF. T\u00f4i r\u1ea5t hoan ngh\u00eanh v\u00e0 \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng d\u0169ng c\u1ea3m \u0111\u00f3 c\u1ee7a anh T\u00fa&quot;.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y nh\u1ea5t, HLV HAGL D\u01b0\u01a1ng Minh Ninh c\u0169ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh vi\u1ec7c b\u1ea7u T\u00fa kh\u00f4ng tranh c\u1eed l\u00e0 tin vui v\u1edbi to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i. &quot;\u0110\u00e2y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 tin r\u1ea5t vui v\u00e0 quan tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng HAGL. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 bi\u1ebft tin n\u00e0y nh\u01b0ng s\u1ebd th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o th\u00eam l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa \u0111\u1ec3 to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i an t\u00e2m v\u00e0 c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ec3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n&rdquo;.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Vi\u1ec7c HAGL ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd \u1edf l\u1ea1i V-League s\u1ebd l\u00e0 tin vui v\u1edbi c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 HAGL. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai thi \u0111\u1ea5u k\u00e9m hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 v\u00ec b\u1ecb ph\u00e2n t\u00e2m b\u1edfi tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng r\u00fat lui c\u1ee7a b\u1ea7u \u0110\u1ee9c. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV HAGL x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;D\u00f9 su\u1ed1t th\u1eddi gian qua l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o ch\u01b0a h\u1ec1 th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o vi\u1ec7c HAGL c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 d\u1eebng cu\u1ed9c ch\u01a1i \u1edf V.League 2018, nh\u01b0ng qua truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng \u00edt nhi\u1ec1u c\u0169ng l\u00e0m c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i xao nh\u00e3ng. Nh\u01b0ng gi\u1edd n\u00e0y khi b\u1ea7u \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh nh\u01b0 v\u1eady th\u00ec to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i s\u1ebd c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ec3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n&quot;, HLV D\u01b0\u01a1ng Minh Ninh t\u00e2m s\u1ef1.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00ec th\u1ebf \u1edf v\u00f2ng t\u1edbi c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 HAGL ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd thi \u0111\u1ea5u 100% phong \u0111\u1ed9 trong chuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch tr\u01b0\u1edbc Qu\u1ea3ng Nam t\u1ea1i Cup QG 2018. \u0110\u00e2y r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f3 m\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai c\u1ea7n thi \u0111\u1ea5u h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c t\u1eadp trung v\u00e0 quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/vleague/bau-tu-rut-lui-vien-canh-cong-phuong-ve-que-lam-ruong-khep-lai-291-185047.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/14/bau-tu-rut-lui-vien-canh-cong-phuong-ve-que-lam-ruong-khep-lai.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/vleague/bau-tu-rut-lui-vien-canh-cong-phuong-ve-que-lam-ruong-khep-lai-291-185047.html\">B\u1ea7u T\u00fa r\u00fat lui, C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n ph\u1ea3i lo v\u1ec1 qu\u00ea l\u00e0m ru\u1ed9ng</span><br>\r\nSau khi b\u1ea7u T\u00fa x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn kh\u00f4ng tham gia \u1ee9ng c\u1eed gh\u1ebf Ph\u00f3 Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch ph\u1ee5 tr\u00e1ch t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh VFF kh\u00f3a t\u1edbi, b\u1ea7u \u0110\u1ee9c nhanh ch\u00f3ng ph\u1ea3n h\u1ed3i v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ec3 C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1ec1 qu\u00ea l\u00e0m...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Thanh Long (TTVN)</p></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"1656","checkdouble":"185053"},{"date":"15:15 26/04","title":"B\u1ed1c th\u0103m VCK U16 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018: U16 Vi\u1ec7t Nam d\u1ec5 th\u1edf, H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u1edf b\u1ea3ng t\u1eed th\u1ea7n","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/12/boc-tham-vck-u16-chau-a-viet-nam-o-bang-de-tho.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margin:0}div.adContainer video{left:0}.adContainer{position:absolute;left:0;top:0;z-index:2}.jp-video-full div.adContainer div{top:0;left:0}.closeAdsbt{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5;cursor:pointer;border-radius:3px;font-weight:bold}.closeAds{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5}.articlerelatepannel{padding:6px;margin-top:5px;margin-bottom:5px;background-color:#f7f7f7;border:solid 1px #069241}.articlerelate{padding:6px;display:lis