splay:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi th\u00e0nh t\u00edch l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong s\u1ed1 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng nh\u00ec b\u1ea3ng c\u00f3 th\u00e0nh t\u00edch t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t \u1edf v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i, \u0110T U16 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 v\u00e9 tham d\u1ef1 VCK U16 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018 s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra t\u1ea1i Malaysia v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i n\u0103m nay.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Boc tham VCK U16 chau A 2018 U16 Viet Nam de tho hinh anh\" title=\"B\u1ed1c th\u0103m VCK U16 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018 U16 Vi\u1ec7t Nam d\u1ec5 th\u1edf h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/12/boc-tham-vck-u16-chau-a-viet-nam-o-bang-de-tho.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>B\u1ed1c th\u0103m VCK U16 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018: U16 Vi\u1ec7t Nam d\u1ec5 th\u1edf</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Do c\u00f3 th\u00e0nh t\u00edch l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1edbi v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u0103m 2016 n\u00ean U16 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u1ebfp \u1edf nh\u00f3m h\u1ea1t gi\u1ed1ng th\u1ee9 2 \u1edf VCK U16 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 n\u0103m nay c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c \u0110T Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n, Oman v\u00e0 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y c\u0169ng gi\u00fap ch\u00fang ta tr\u00e1nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c hai '\u00f4ng k\u1eb9' H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c, Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n ngay \u1edf v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u b\u1ea3ng.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u1ed1c th\u0103m U16 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 di\u1ec5n ra chi\u1ec1u nay 26/4, \u0110T U16 Vi\u1ec7t Nam r\u01a1i v\u00e0o b\u1ea3ng C c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i Iran, \u1ea4n \u0110\u1ed9 v\u00e0 Indonesia.\u00a0</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e2y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1eeba s\u1ee9c v\u1edbi c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb Vi\u1ec7t Nam trong m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau gi\u00e0nh quy\u1ec1n v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft v\u00e0 xa h\u01a1n l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t su\u1ea5t v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft c\u00f9ng t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 d\u1ef1 World Cup U17. Ngo\u1ea1i tr\u1eeb \u0110T U16 Iran \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n th\u00ec ch\u00fang ta ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i hai \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i.\u00a0</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong khi \u0111\u00f3 \u1edf b\u1ea3ng A, ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Malaysia s\u1ebd c\u00f9ng b\u1ea3ng Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n, Th\u00e1i Lan v\u00e0 Tajikistan. K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u1ed1c th\u0103m n\u00e0y c\u00f3 l\u1ee3i cho Th\u00e1i Lan b\u1edfi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ea1nh tranh tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft l\u00e0 Tajikistan c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 m\u1ea1nh.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Viet Nam o bang dau vua phai tai le boc tham VCK U16 chau A 2018\" title=\"Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u1edf b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1eeba ph\u1ea3i t\u1ea1i l\u1ec5 b\u1ed1c th\u0103m VCK U16 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/26/DbsUTCsWkAAiiD6.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>U16 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u1edf b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1eeba ph\u1ea3i t\u1ea1i l\u1ec5 b\u1ed1c th\u0103m VCK U16 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong khi \u0111\u00f3 b\u1ea3ng B g\u1ed3m Tri\u1ec1u Ti\u00ean, Yemen, Oman v\u00e0 Jordan c\u00f2n b\u1ea3ng D \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1eed th\u1ea7n \u1edf gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m nay khi \u0110KV\u0110 Iraq s\u1ebd ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c, Australia v\u00e0 Afghanistan.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Gi\u1ea3i U16 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018 s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra t\u1eeb 20/9 \u0111\u1ebfn 7/10 t\u1ea1i Malaysia. B\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft s\u1ebd l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n cho ch\u00e2u \u00c1 d\u1ef1 World Cup U17 t\u1ea1i Peru n\u0103m 2019.\u00a0</p>\r\nM\u1ea1nh C\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"1655","checkdouble":"185054"},{"date":"15:53 26/04","title":"HLV Nguy\u1ec5n Th\u00e0nh Vinh tr\u00e1ch Thanh H\u00f3a \u201cx\u1eed ph\u0169\u201d B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/16/hlv-nguyen-thanh-vinh-trach-thanh-hoa-xu-phu-bui-tien-dung.jpeg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margin:0}div.adContainer video{left:0}.adContainer{position:absolute;left:0;top:0;z-index:2}.jp-video-full div.a