=50)}.ui-widget-shadow{margin:-5px 0 0 -5px;padding:5px;background:#000 url(images/ui-bg_flat_10_000000_40x100.png) 50% 50% repeat-x;opacity:.2;filter:Alpha(Opacity=20);border-radius:5px}.link-web>a{color:#555;font-size:12px;line-height:24px}body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau khi HLV Mihail xin t\u1eeb ch\u1ee9c v\u00ec kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ecbu \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00e1i \u0111\u1ed9 b\u1ea5t tu\u00e2n l\u1ec7nh c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 FLC Thanh H\u00f3a, th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng c\u0169ng gi\u00e1n ti\u1ebfp 'g\u1eb7p h\u1ecda'.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tin d\u00f9ng, ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111ang ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3i qua chu\u1ed7i ng\u00e0y th\u00e1ng \u0111en t\u1ed1i \u1edf x\u1ee9 Thanh v\u1edbi 4 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb.\u00a0</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">4 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u FLC Thanh H\u00f3a 'kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n' th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 n\u1ed5i 1 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng, v\u1edbi 4 tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp, ghi 10 b\u00e0n v\u00e0 c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ecdt l\u01b0\u1edbi 10 b\u00e0n.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Nguyen Thanh Vinh\" title=\"HLV Nguy\u1ec5n Th\u00e0nh Vinh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2015/3/28/u23-viet-nam-co-the-nhat-bang-i.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HLV Nguy\u1ec5n Th\u00e0nh Vinh\u00a0tr\u00e1ch BHL Thanh H\u00f3a \u0111\u00e3 x\u1eed l\u00fd kh\u00f4ng kh\u00e9o v\u1edbi B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn chuy\u1ec7n n\u00e0y, m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n k\u1ef3 c\u1ef1u HLV Nguy\u1ec5n Th\u00e0nh Vinh \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng cho r\u1eb1ng BHL FLC Thanh H\u00f3a c\u1ea7n ch\u00eca ra m\u1ed9t c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb tr\u00ean b\u00e1o D\u00e2n Vi\u1ec7t, HLV Nguy\u1ec5n Thanh Vinh t\u00e2m s\u1ef1: \u201cHLV ng\u01b0\u1eddi Romania Marian Mihail t\u1eebng r\u1ea5t hi\u1ec3u t\u1ea7m quan tr\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi CLB v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb7t ni\u1ec1m tin v\u00e0o D\u0169ng. Nh\u01b0ng sau khi HLV n\u00e0y 'm\u1ea5t gh\u1ebf', FLC Thanh H\u00f3a \u0111\u00e3 x\u1eed l\u00fd kh\u00f4ng kh\u00e9o v\u1edbi Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi con c\u1ee7a Thanh H\u00f3a, l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t t\u00e0i n\u0103ng, l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00e0 c\u1ea7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ea1o \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n, ch\u0103m s\u00f3c, b\u1ed3i d\u01b0\u1ee1ng \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u00e1t huy h\u1ebft kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">FLC Thanh H\u00f3a c\u1ea7n nh\u1eafc nh\u1edf Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng t\u1eadp trung v\u00e0o chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, gi\u00fap c\u1eadu ta \u00fd th\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m ngh\u1ec1 nghi\u1ec7p v\u1edbi t\u01b0 c\u00e1ch l\u00e0 1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t, m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n quan tr\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng qu\u00ea h\u01b0\u01a1ng, thay v\u00ec 'th\u1ea3 l\u1ecfng' Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t 'ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1eeba', ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn v\u1ecb tr\u00ed d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb. Nh\u01b0 v\u1eady Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng s\u1ebd n\u1ea3n v\u00e0 thui ch\u1ed9t m\u1ea5t\u201d.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, Thanh H\u00f3a s\u1ebd c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Long An t\u1ea1i Cup Qu\u1ed1c gia, hy v\u1ecdng \u1edf tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y BHL FLC Thanh H\u00f3a s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ec3 B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng ra s\u00e2n. \u0110\u00e2y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng t\u00ecm l\u1ea1i c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c thi \u0111\u1ea5u sau nh\u1eefng l\u00f9m x\u00f9m v\u1eeba qua.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-thanh-hoa-noi-gi-khi-bui-tien-dung-tiep-tuc-ngoi-du-bi-168-185021.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/25/hlv-thanh-hoa-noi-gi-khi-bui-tien-dung-tiep-tuc-ngoi-du-bi.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-thanh-hoa-noi-gi-khi-bui-tien-dung-tiep-tuc-ngoi-du-bi-168-185021.html\">HLV Thanh H\u00f3a n\u00f3i g\u00ec khi B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb?</span><br>\r\nPh\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd HLV FLC Thanh H\u00f3a \u0111\u00e3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh vi\u1ec7c l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh tr\u01b0\u1edbc Yangon United ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n d\u1ef1a tr\u00ean phong \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00e0...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Thanh Long (TTVN)</p></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"1654","checkdouble":"185056"},{"date":"17:42 26/04","title":"Th\u1ee7 l\u0129nh \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ea1i g\u1eb7p Th\u00e1i Lan 