9t trong nh\u1eefng \u1ee9ng c\u1eed vi\u00ean s\u00e1ng gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t. Nh\u01b0ng m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u00f4ng v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 ch\u00fat li\u00ean h\u1ec7 tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp n\u00e0o v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London.<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Su that vu Simeone den Arsenal thay Wenger hinh anh\" title=\"S\u1ef1 th\u1eadt v\u1ee5 Simeone \u0111\u1ebfn Arsenal thay Wenger h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/26/simeone-noi-gi-truoc-co-hoi-den-arsenal-thay-wenger.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Simeone \u0111\u1ebfn Arsenal thay Wenger?</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nKhi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1nh b\u00e1o ch\u00ed h\u1ecfi \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 ai \u1edf Arsenal ch\u01b0a, Simeone kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn: <em>\u201cKh\u00f4ng, t\u00f4i ch\u01b0a n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi ai \u1edf Arsenal c\u1ea3\u201d.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201c\u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean hi\u1ec7n l\u00ean trong suy ngh\u0129 c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 ng\u01b0\u1ee1ng m\u1ed9 d\u00e0nh cho HLV Wenger. \u00d4ng \u1ea5y lu\u00f4n c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n m\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u ho\u00e0n c\u1ea3nh kh\u00e1c nhau ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i th\u1ea5y m\u00ecnh l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t HLV tr\u1ebb v\u00e0 t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n quan s\u00e1t v\u00e0 h\u1ecdc h\u1ecfi t\u1eeb Wenger. V\u1ecb th\u1ebf m\u00e0 \u00f4ng \u1ea5y c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trong l\u00e0ng b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 th\u1eadt \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cV\u1edbi t\u00ecnh y\u00eau m\u00e0 Wenger d\u00e0nh cho Arsenal, \u00f4ng \u1ea5y lu\u00f4n mu\u1ed1n nh\u00ecn th\u1ea5y \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng. H\u1ecdc h\u1ecfi t\u1eeb m\u1ed9t HLV l\u00e3o luy\u1ec7n nh\u01b0 Wenger lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u s\u1eafp t\u1edbi, HLV Simeone cho bi\u1ebft: <em>\u201cT\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111ang c\u00f3 tinh th\u1ea7n s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng. Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Arsenal \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i t\u1eadp trung cao \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00e0 ch\u01a1i v\u1edbi kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t m\u00ecnh c\u00f3\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Gary Neville cho r\u1eb1ng Arsenal n\u00ean b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m Diego Simeone n\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 mu\u1ed1n c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Premier League trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai. \u0110\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n l\u00e0 b\u1edfi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t HLV c\u00f3 c\u00e1 t\u00ednh v\u00e0 b\u1ea3n l\u0129nh d\u1eabn d\u1eaft. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nSo v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng chi ti\u00eau, Arsenal kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 so \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ea1nh tranh \u1edf Premier League. V\u1eady n\u00ean, h\u1ecd b\u1eaft bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t HLV ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng n\u1ebfu mu\u1ed1n gi\u00e0nh ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch \u1edf c\u00e1c gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa Arsenal v\u00e0 Atletico c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 coi l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft s\u1edbm \u1edf Europa League m\u00f9a n\u00e0y. \u1ede c\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i, Marseille \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi Red Bull Salzburg v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 qu\u00e1 cao.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam th\u00f4ng tin tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn Arsenal vs Atletico:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/nhan-dinh-arsenal-vs-atletico-madrid-2h05-ngay-274-tat-ca-vi-wenger-184-185040.html\">Arsenal vs Atletico Madrid (2h05 ng\u00e0y 27/4): T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 v\u00ec Wenger</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/arsenal-vo-dich-europa-league-la-mon-qua-chia-tay-wenger-184-184904.html\">Arsenal v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Europa League l\u00e0 m\u00f3n qu\u00e0 chia tay Wenger</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"1652","checkdouble":"185044"},{"date":"12:00 26/04","title":"Kimmich: \"\u0110\u00e1ng l\u1ebd t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 7-2 nghi\u00eang v\u1ec1 Bayern\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/26/kimmich-dang-le-ty-so-phai-la-72-nghieng-ve-bayern.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margin:0}div.adContainer video{left:0}.adContainer{position:absolute;left:0;top:0;z-index:2