;filter:Alpha(Opacity=50)}.ui-widget-shadow{margin:-5px 0 0 -5px;padding:5px;background:#000 url(images/ui-bg_flat_10_000000_40x100.png) 50% 50% repeat-x;opacity:.2;filter:Alpha(Opacity=20);border-radius:5px}.link-web>a{color:#555;font-size:12px;line-height:24px}body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Bayern Munich d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i</h2>\r\n<div><br>\r\nTrong tr\u1eadn ti\u1ebfp Real Madrid \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i b\u00e1n k\u1ebft Champions League, Bayern Munich l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n. \u201cH\u00f9m x\u00e1m\u201d c\u1ea7m b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ebfn 60% v\u00e0 d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m g\u1ea5p g\u1ea7n 3 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 h\u1ecd d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m 17 l\u1ea7n so v\u1edbi 7 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch.</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Joshua Kimmich noi ve tran Bayern Munich vs Real Madrid hinh anh\" title=\"Joshua Kimmich n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Bayern Munich vs Real Madrid h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/26/Joshua-Kimmich-noi-ve-tran-Bayern-Munich-vs-Real-Madrid-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Bayern thua Real 1-2 ngay tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nM\u1eb7c d\u00f9 d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u nh\u01b0ng Bayern v\u1eabn \u0111\u1ec3 thua v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 1-2, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-chau-au/ket-qua-bayern-munich-vs-real-madrid-tran-dau-luot-di-ban-ket-champions-league-201718-184-185015.html\" target=\"_blank\">k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 Bayern Munich vs Real Madrid</span> khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110\u1ee9c g\u1eb7p r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n \u1edf tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1.</div>\r\n<div><br>\r\nJoshua Kimmich n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Bayern Munich vs Real Madrid, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i m\u00e0 hai \u0111\u1ed9i c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1ng l\u1ebd ra \u201cH\u00f9m x\u00e1m\u201d ph\u1ea3i th\u1eafng v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 7-2.</div>\r\n<div><br>\r\n\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o ra r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i, trong \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng \u00edt nh\u1eefng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng. Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng v\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng. Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i k\u00e9m h\u01a1n l\u00e0 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn ch\u00fang t\u00f4i th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y\u201d.</div>\r\n<div><br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd v\u1edbi quan \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i, b\u1edfi n\u1ebfu t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng t\u1ed1t nh\u1eefng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e1ng l\u1ebd ra Bayern Munich ph\u1ea3i gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 7-2\u201d.</div>\r\n<div><br>\r\nH\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Niklas Sule c\u0169ng than phi\u1ec1n v\u1edbi kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0: \u201cReal c\u00f3 2 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng v\u00e0 ghi 2 b\u00e0n trong khi \u0111\u00f3 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i phung ph\u00ed qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i, n\u1ebfu d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1ed1t Bayern \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 5-2\u201d.</div>\r\n<div>\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Kimmich th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng b\u1edfi Robben r\u1eddi s\u00e2n s\u1edbm</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div>Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Robben ch\u1ec9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f3 v\u00e0i ph\u00fat tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi r\u1eddi s\u00e2n v\u00ec ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ea5t m\u00e1t kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ecf v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 b\u1edfi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0 Lan \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Bayern Munich.</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Kimmich noi ve tran Bayern vs Real\" title=\"Kimmich n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Bayern vs Real\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/26/kimmich-dang-le-ty-so-phai-la-72-nghieng-ve-bayern.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Kimmich n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Bayern vs Real</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nJoshua Kimmich c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y r\u1ea5t cay \u0111\u1eafng khi Robben r\u1eddi s\u00e2n s\u1edbm: \u201cT\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y r\u1ea5t ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i khi anh \u1ea5y ph\u1ea3i r\u1eddi s\u00e2n qu\u00e1 s\u1edbm. Anh \u1ea5y l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi thu h\u00fat v\u00e0 t\u1ea1o kh\u00f4ng gian cho t\u00f4i, gi\u00fap t\u00f4i c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i tham gia t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng h\u01a1n\u201d.</div>\r\n<div><br>\r\n\u201cThomas Muller \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng l\u00e0m t\u1ed1t nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 \u0111\u00f3, anh \u1ea5y c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean l\u00f9i v\u1ec1 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn Real c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u th\u1eddi gian v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng gian \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng\u201d.</div>\r\n<div><br>\r\n<strong>Phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Joshua Kimmich \u1edf Bundesliga 2017/18</strong></div>\r\n<div><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://sja.sportradar.com/w/Bongda24H/259117-41576/033100\" rel=\"nofollow\">Phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Joshua Kimmich \u1edf Bundesliga 2017/18</span></div>\r\n<div><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div>\u00a0</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"1651","checkdouble":"185048"},{"date":"13:09 26/04","title":"4 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 4 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i sau tr\u1eadn Bayern Munich 1-2 Real Madrid","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/26/4-nguoi-chien-thang-va-4-nguoi-that-bai-sau-tran-bayern-munich-12-real-madrid.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margin:0}div.adContainer video{left:0}.adContainer{position:absolute;left:0;top:0;z-index:2}.jp-video-full div.adContainer div{top:0;left:0}.closeAdsbt{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-co