0% 50% repeat-x;opacity:.2;filter:Alpha(Opacity=20);border-radius:5px}.link-web>a{color:#555;font-size:12px;line-height:24px}body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng: Nh\u1eefng h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u1eefng h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh c\u1ee7a hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 Marcelo b\u00ean ph\u00eda Real Madrid v\u00e0 Joshua Kimmich b\u00ean ph\u00eda \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0. H\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1edf c\u1ea3 kh\u00eda c\u1ea1nh t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng l\u1eabn ph\u00f2ng th\u1ee7.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Bayern Munich vs Real Madrid ban ket Champions League hinh anh\" title=\"Bayern Munich vs Real Madrid b\u00e1n k\u1ebft Champions League h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/26/Bayern-Munich-vs-Real-Madrid-ban-ket-Champions-League-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Marcelo v\u00e0 Kimmich c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nKimmich l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 cho Bayern, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng th\u1ee9 100 c\u1ee7a &ldquo;H\u00f9m x\u00e1m&rdquo; d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Jupp Heynckes t\u1ea1i Champions League. Kimmich \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i d\u1ea5u \u1ea5n v\u00e0o 19 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng (5 b\u00e0n, 14 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o) \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nCh\u1ec9 c\u00f3 Lewandowski (42) v\u00e0 Muller (29) l\u00e0 c\u00f3 \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n Kimmich. T\u1ea1i Champions League m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1995 c\u00f3 3 b\u00e0n v\u00e0 3 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMarcelo sau \u0111\u00f3 g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a 1-1 cho Real v\u1edbi c\u00fa \u0111\u00e1 v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng hi\u1ec3m h\u00f3c khi\u1ebfn th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 bi\u1ebft \u0111\u1ee9ng nh\u00ecn. Marcelo \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 7 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng knock-out Champions League, nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 n\u00e0o.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y, anh ghi 3 b\u00e0n \u1edf Champions League v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u lo\u1ea1i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp (v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi PSG, Juve, Bayern). Trong 33 tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil ghi b\u00e0n, Real Madrid gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 32 l\u1ea7n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Asensio&nbsp;</h2>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Zidane kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a Isco bu\u1ed9c \u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u01b0a ra nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i, Asensio \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng khi\u1ebfn \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh ph\u1ea3i th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Asensio ghi ban cho Real truoc Bayern\" title=\"Asensio ghi ban cho Real truoc Bayern\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/26/Joshua-Kimmich-noi-ve-tran-Bayern-Munich-vs-Real-Madrid-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Asensio ghi b\u00e0n \u1ea5n \u0111\u1ecbnh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-1 cho Real Madrid</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nCh\u00ednh Marco Asensio l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ghi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u1edf ph\u00fat 57 gi\u00fap Real Madrid c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 2-1. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1996 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng t\u1ea1i Champions League m\u00f9a n\u00e0y, c\u1ea3 3 \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ebfn khi anh v\u00e0o s\u00e2n thay ng\u01b0\u1eddi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi s\u1ef1 tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh v\u01b0\u1ee3t b\u1eadc, Asensio \u0111ang chi\u1ebfm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ni\u1ec1m tin t\u1eeb ph\u00eda HLV Zidane. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111ang d\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea9y Gareth Bale kh\u1ecfi s\u00e2n Bernabeu.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Real Madrid</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Real Madrid l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u00e1n m\u1ed1c 150 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng t\u1ea1i Champions League. V\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i so v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ebfp sau bao g\u1ed3m Barca (138),&nbsp;Bayern (128), MU (114) v\u00e0 Juventus (87).<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Real Madrid chiem loi the lon truoc tran luot ve\" title=\"Real Madrid chi\u1ebfm l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf l\u1edbn tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/26/real-maddird.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Real Madrid chi\u1ebfm l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf l\u1edbn tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nReal Madrid l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League, h\u1ecd \u0111ang \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u00f3 l\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 3 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nLos Blancos c\u00e0ng ch\u01a1i c\u00e0ng hay \u1edf Champions League m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y. V\u1edbi th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i 2-1 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Bayern Munich, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Bernabeu \u0111ang chi\u1ebfm l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf l\u1edbn tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u00e1nh c\u1eeda v\u00e0o ch\u01a1i tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft \u0111\u00e3 m\u1edf toang ph\u00eda tr\u01b0\u1edbc HLV Zidane v\u00e0 c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2. N\u1ebfu v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Real s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 Liverpool, v\u1edbi kinh nghi\u1ec7m c\u00f9ng b\u1ea3n l\u0129nh K\u1ec1n k\u1ec1n tr\u1eafng \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i The Kop.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>HLV Zinedine Zidane</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">So v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed9 tu\u1ed5i, HLV Zinedine Zidane r\u1ea5t khi\u00eam t\u1ed1n n\u1ebfu \u0111\u1eb7t c\u1ea1nh Jupp Heynckes, song v\u1ecb chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p \u0111ang cho th\u1ea5y \u00f4ng kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 thua k\u00e9m v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t t\u00e0i n\u0103ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Zinedine Zidane\" title=\"HLV Zinedine Zidane\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/26/HLV-Zidane.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Zinedine Zidane g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nL\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i h\u1ee3p l\u00fd \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap Real Madrid h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u s\u1ef1 nguy hi\u1ec3m t\u1eeb ph\u00eda \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0, nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 thay th\u1ebf t\u1eeb Zidane c\u0169ng t\u1ecf ra h\u1ee3p l\u00fd h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n Heynckes, b\u1eb1ng ch\u1ee9ng l\u00e0 Asensio, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u00e0o s\u00e2n thay ng\u01b0\u1eddi ghi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-1 \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i, Real c\u1ee7a Zidane \u0111ang chi\u1ebfm l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1. \u00d4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng x\u1ee9ng \u0111ang nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi khen t\u1eeb Heynckes: &ldquo;Zidane r\u1ea5t t\u00e0i n\u0103ng, t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao \u00f4ng \u1ea5y&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nZidane \u0111ang khi\u1ebfn ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta ph\u1ea3i \u0111i t\u1eeb b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ebfn b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd kh\u00e1c, \u00f4ng s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eafc \u0111\u1ebfn r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u n\u1eefa n\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 gi\u00fap Real Madrid v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League 3 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i: Bayern Munich</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 nh\u01b0ng Bayern Munich l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ec3 Real Madrid \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 2-1, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-chau-au/ket-qua-bayern-munich-vs-real-madrid-tran-dau-luot-di-ban-ket-champions-league-201718-184-185015.html\" target=\"_blank\">k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Bayern Munich vs Real Madrid</span> khi\u1ebfn c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u00e0o ch\u01a1i tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft c\u1ee7a &ldquo;H\u00f9m x\u00e1m&rdquo; nh\u1ecf \u0111i tr\u00f4ng th\u1ea5y.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"James Rodriguez noi ve tran Bayern vs Real\" title=\"James Rodriguez n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Bayern vs Real\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/26/james-rodriguez-noi-gi-sau-tran-thua-cua-bayern-truoc-real.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Bayern \u0111\u1ec3 thua 1-2 ngay tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nBayern \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u k\u00e9m c\u1ecfi \u1edf c\u1ea3 kh\u00eda c\u1ea1nh t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng l\u1eabn ph\u00f2ng th\u1ee7. N\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng phung ph\u00ed c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i th\u00ec h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 l\u1ea1i m\u1eafc nh\u1eefng sai l\u1ea7m tai h\u1ea1i. HLV Jupp Heynckes kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh &ldquo;H\u00f9m x\u00e1m&rdquo; \u0111\u00e3 bi\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng cho Real 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Real, Bayern Munich c\u00f2n nh\u1eadn t\u1ed5n th\u1ea5t l\u1edbn v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng. Theo \u0111\u00f3 Arjen Robben v\u00e0 Jerome Boateng ph\u1ea3i r\u1eddi s\u00e2n t\u1eeb kh\u00e1 s\u1edbm.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nB\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Bayern Munich d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng kh\u00e1 nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed Boateng c\u00f2n \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 tham d\u1ef1 VCK World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Gareth Bale</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Bayern Munich vs Real Madrid b\u00e1n k\u1ebft Champions League, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Gareth Bale ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb. HLV Zidane s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng b\u1ed9 ba t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng Isco, Ronaldo v\u00e0 Vazquez, sau \u0111\u00f3 \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p t\u1ea1o ra s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i nh\u01b0ng Bale kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Bale roi Real\" title=\"Bale r\u1eddi Real\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/26/tiep-tuc-bi-zidane-bo-roi-gareth-bale-cay-cu-doi-den-bayern.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Bale c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u1eddi Real \u0111\u1ebfn Bayern \u1edf H\u00e8 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo \u0111\u00f3, Asensio v\u00e0 Benzema \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn ch\u1ee9 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi x\u1ee9 Wales. \u0110\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y Bale b\u1ecb Zidane b\u1ecf r\u01a1i. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 trong hai tr\u1eadn t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft v\u1edbi Juventus anh ch\u1ec9 ra s\u00e2n 45 ph\u00fat.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 n\u1eefa, \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8 g\u1eb7p PSG Bale \u0111\u1ec1u ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb. Vi\u1ec7c kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean \u0111ang khi\u1ebfn Bale th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi x\u1ee9 Wales th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Bayern Munich \u1edf H\u00e8 2018.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>H\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng Bayern Munich</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Bayern Munich \u0111\u00e3 d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i so v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch. H\u1ecd th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n t\u1edbi 17 pha h\u00e3m th\u00e0nh, trong \u0111\u00f3 5 tr\u00fang \u0111\u00edch trong khi \u0111\u00f3 trong 90 ph\u00fat thi \u0111\u1ea5u Real Madrid ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 7 pha d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Bayern vs Real Modric Ribery di bong\" title=\"Bayern vs Real Modric Ribery di bong\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/25/nhan-dinh-bayern-vs-real-1h45-ngay-264-vi-champions-league-khong-phai-bundesliga.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ribery d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m 4 l\u1ea7n nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ghi b\u00e0n</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1eb7c d\u00f9 s\u1ed1 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u1eefng c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i nh\u01b0ng Bayern ch\u1ec9 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 1 b\u00e0n trong khi Real l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1ea5p \u0111\u00f4i s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f3, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 cho th\u1ea5y kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch l\u00e0 t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMarcelo v\u00e0 Asensio m\u1ed7i ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec1u chuy\u1ec3n h\u00f3a th\u00e0nh b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, trong khi \u0111\u00f3 b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i Robert Lewandowski v\u00e0 Franck Ribery m\u1ed7i ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m 4 l\u1ea7n nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ghi b\u00e0n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nVi\u1ec7c h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn Bayern ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i. H\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Niklas Sule kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh n\u1ebfu t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng t\u1ed1t c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i Bayern \u0111\u00e3 th\u1eafng 5-2 c\u00f2n Joshua Kimmich th\u00ec kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 7-2 nghi\u00eang v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Keylor Navas</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Keylor Navas \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Bayern vs Real b\u00e1n k\u1ebft l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i Champions League. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Costa Rica m\u1eafc l\u1ed7i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp trong b\u00e0n m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 c\u1ee7a Bayern Munich.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Keylor Navas khong hoan thanh nhiem vu\" title=\"Keylor Navas kh\u00f4ng ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/26/navas.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Keylor Navas kh\u00f4ng ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nPh\u00fat 28, Kimmich b\u0103ng xu\u1ed1ng tr\u1ed1ng tr\u1ea3i b\u00ean c\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i, Navas \u0111\u00e3 ph\u00e1n \u0111o\u00e1n sai khi b\u0103ng ra \u1eaft b\u00e0i \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n ngang c\u1ee7a h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c nh\u01b0ng r\u1ed1t cu\u1ed9c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 23 tu\u1ed5i s\u00fat th\u1eb3ng v\u00e0 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n c\u1ee7a Real kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ng\u0103n c\u1ea3n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nCh\u1eafc ch\u1eafn HLV Zidane v\u00e0 BL\u0110 Real kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n n\u00e0y. T\u1edd Don Balon c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y Ban Nha kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh gi\u1edd ngh\u1ec9 gi\u1eefa hi\u1ec7p, Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng b\u1ee9c x\u00fac, anh mu\u1ed1n Los Blancos mua De Gea thay Navas.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"1650","checkdouble":"185050"},{"date":"15:52 26/04","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Marseille vs Salzburg 02h05 ng\u00e0y 27/4 (Europa League 2017/18)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/4/26/nhan-dinh-marseille-vs-salzburg-02h05-ngay-274-europa-league-201718.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margin:0}div.adContainer video{left:0}.adContainer{position:absolute;left:0;top:0;z-index:2}.jp-video-full div.adContainer div{top:0;left:0}.closeAdsbt{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5;cursor:pointer;border-radius:3px;font-weight:bold}.closeAds{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5}.articlerelatepannel{padding:6px;margin