 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nhan dinh Marseille vs Salzburg 2h05 ngay 274 Europa League 2018 hinh anh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Marseille vs Salzburg 2h05 ng\u00e0y 274 Europa League 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/26/mar-sal.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Marseille vs Salzburg</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; text-align: justify;\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Marseille vs Salzburg: 2-0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Salzburg l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong ba \u0111\u1ed9i b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng v\u00e0 h\u1ecd l\u1eb7ng l\u1ebd v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua m\u1ecdi ch\u01b0\u1edbng ng\u1ea1i v\u1eadt \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng 4 \u0111\u1ed9i xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t Europa League m\u00f9a n\u00e0y. Th\u1eafng tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Dortmund r\u1ed3i th\u1ee7 h\u00f2a \u1edf tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 1/8, sau \u0111\u00f3 Salzburg l\u1ed9i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng g\u00e2y s\u1ed1c tr\u01b0\u1edbc Lazio \u1edf t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft. \u0110\u1ea5y l\u00e0 ch\u01b0a k\u1ec3 \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/16, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u00c1o c\u0169ng v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n h\u1ecd l\u00e0 Sociedad. C\u0169ng c\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5n m\u1ea1nh, Salzburg ch\u1eb3ng c\u00f2n l\u1ea1 g\u00ec Marseille, \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 m\u00e0 h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng thua khi hai \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n nhau \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng m\u00f9a n\u00e0y (1 th\u1eafng, 1 h\u00f2a). <br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0 th\u1ebf, Salzburg \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1ea3i qua \u0111\u1ee7 m\u1ecdi l\u1eb1n ranh sinh t\u1eed \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 g\u00e2y b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd tr\u01b0\u1edbc b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u00c1o \u0111ang c\u00f3 16 tr\u1eadn b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i t\u1ea1i 17 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i Europa League. \u201cSalzburg r\u1ea5t m\u1ea1nh. H\u1ecd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u00c1o mang tinh th\u1ea7n \u0110\u1ee9c. Marseille ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n t\u1ea1i Velodrome \u0111\u00eam nay. Nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua h\u1ecd \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1\u201d, HLV Rudi Garcia c\u1ee7a Marseille ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u tr\u01b0\u1edbc gi\u1edd G.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00eam nay, Marseille c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Bouna Sarr v\u00e0 Rolando. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 b\u1ed5 sung gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ph\u1ea3i Hiroki Sakai ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u 3 tu\u1ea7n. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a Luiz Gustavo s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 s\u1edf tr\u01b0\u1eddng, kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00f9i xu\u1ed1ng ch\u01a1i trung v\u1ec7 nh\u01b0 su\u1ed1t h\u01a1n 1 th\u00e1ng qua. Ngo\u00e0i ra, Jordan Amavi c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 sung s\u1ee9c tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i sau th\u1eddi gian d\u01b0\u1ee1ng th\u01b0\u01a1ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi nh\u1eefng thay \u0111\u1ed5i nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1 \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd n\u00e0y, HLV Rudi Garcia c\u0169ng c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 4-2-3-1 s\u1edf tr\u01b0\u1eddng v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 th\u0103ng hoa c\u1ee7a Florian Thauvin v\u00e0 Dimitri Payet. \u1ede tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng Europa League m\u00f9a n\u00e0y tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Velodrome, Marseille kh\u00f4ng bung h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c tr\u01b0\u1edbc Salzburg v\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng knock-out. Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u0111\u00eam nay t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 s\u1ebd kh\u00e1c. B\u1edfi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u s\u1ed1ng c\u00f2n. V\u00e0 Marseille s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ee1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i gi\u00e0nh th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n21 - Marseille ch\u1ec9 thua 1 l\u1ea7n \u1edf 21 tr\u1eadn s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 2-3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Lyon t\u1ea1i Ligue 1 v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 19/3 v\u1eeba qua. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, Salzburg c\u0169ng m\u1edbi thua 2 tr\u1eadn \u1edf 21 chuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTH\u00d4NG TIN XUNG QUANH<br>\r\n- Theo ch\u00e2u \u00c1, Marseille th\u1eafng 9, h\u00f2a 3, thua 8 \u1edf 20 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t; Salzburg th\u1eafng 13, h\u00f2a 1, thua 6 \u1edf 20 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y.<br>\r\n- Tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0, Marseille th\u1eafng 11, h\u00f2a 1, thua 8 \u1edf 20 tr\u1eadn v\u1eeba qua theo ch\u00e2u \u00c1.<br>\r\n- Tr\u00ean s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch, Salzburg th\u1eafng 10, h\u00f2a 1, thua 9 \u1edf 20 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t theo ch\u00e2u \u00c1.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1eb6C BI\u1ec6T<br>\r\nL\u01b0\u1edbi rung cu\u1ed1i hi\u1ec7p 1<br>\r\n19/20 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Marseille v\u00e0 5/7 chuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y c\u1ee7a Salzburg c\u00f3 \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng t\u1eeb ph\u00fat 16-45. Ngo\u00e0i ra, 9/10 tr\u1eadn s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 v\u1eeba qua c\u1ee7a Marseille c\u0169ng ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn t\u1ed1i thi\u1ec3u 1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u1edf 30 ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i hi\u1ec7p 1.</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo Bongdaplus.vn<br></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"1649","checkdouble":"185055"},{"date":"14:47 26/04","title":"Real quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m c\u00f3 b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c sao Liverpool \u1edf H\u00e8 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/2/25/real-quyet-tam-co-bang-duoc-sao-liverpool-o-he-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margin:0}div.adContainer video{left:0}.adContainer{position:absolute;left:0;top:0;z-index:2}.jp-video-full div.adContainer div{top:0;left:0}.closeAdsbt{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5;cursor:pointer;border-radius:3px;font-weight:bold}.closeAds{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5}.art