latepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Emre Can t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i gia h\u1ea1n v\u1edbi Liverpool</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nH\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Emre Can v\u1edbi Liverpool c\u00f2n th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ebfn H\u00e8 2018, d\u00f9 Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1994 gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Real Madrid mua Emre Can o ky chuyen nhuong He 2018 hinh anh\" title=\"Real Madrid mua Emre Can \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/18/Real-Madrid-mua-Emre-Can-o-ky-chuyen-nhuong-He-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Emre Can mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Liverpool \u1edf H\u00e8 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nNh\u1eefng b\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n \u1edf b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi khi\u1ebfn The Kop \u0111ang b\u1ebf t\u1eafc trong vi\u1ec7c gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c. Theo The Sun, Can\u00a0\u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i gia h\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra \u0111i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHLV Klopp \u0111\u00e3 th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1994 r\u1eddi Anfield \u1edf H\u00e8 n\u00e0y, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh d\u00f9 Can c\u00f3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh th\u1ebf n\u00e0o th\u00ec \u00f4ng v\u1eabn t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHi\u1ec7n c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 23 tu\u1ed5i, trong \u0111\u00f3 ph\u1ea3i k\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ebfn Juventus. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin \u0111\u00e3 c\u1eed ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ebfn Anh \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n. Ngo\u00e0i ra hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Manchester v\u00e0 PSG c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Real Madrid quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Emre Can</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/real-bat-ngo-muon-chieu-mo-cau-thu-liverpool-180-174825.html\" target=\"_blank\">Real Madrid mua Emre Can</span> \u1edf H\u00e8 2018, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Bernabeu mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Emre Can\" title=\"Emre Can\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/1/18/Bayern-mua-Emre-Can-o-ky-chuyen-nhuong-He-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Real Madrid quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Emre Can</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nLos Blancos \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p \u1edf H\u00e8 n\u00e0y, h\u1ecd nh\u1eafm Can nh\u01b0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u thay th\u1ebf Luka Modric. Real ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Bernabeu c\u0169ng h\u1ee9a s\u1ebd t\u1ea1o \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean. Theo Don Balon, Real s\u1ebd c\u1eed ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u00ed m\u1eadt \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 23 tu\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u00e0i n\u0103ng v\u00e0 c\u00f2n r\u1ea5t tr\u1ebb, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t c\u00f2n c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 0 \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 \u0111ang khi\u1ebfn nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e8m kh\u00e1t.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong m\u1ed9t ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ecfi v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh Can kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh: \u201cT\u00f4i ch\u01b0a \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o c\u1ea3, t\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i, hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i t\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 t\u1eadp trung v\u00e0o thi \u0111\u1ea5u\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nCh\u01b0a bi\u1ebft l\u00e0 Emre Can s\u1ebd c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o ch\u1ec9 bi\u1ebft r\u1eb1ng cu\u1ed9c chi\u1ebfn gi\u00e0nh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra c\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng v\u00e0 quy\u1ebft li\u1ec7t.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)<br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"1648","checkdouble":"185052"},{"date":"12:18 26/04","title":"Man City c\u00f3 \u0111\u00f4i l\u1eddi nh\u1eafn g\u1eedi \u0111\u1ebfn Real Madrid?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/26/man-city-co-doi-loi-nhan-gui-den-real-madrid.PNG","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margin:0}div.adContainer video{left:0}.adContainer{position:absolute;left:0;top:0;z-index:2}.jp-video-full div.adContainer div{top:0;left:0}.closeAdsbt{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5;cursor:pointer;border-radius:3px;font-weight:bold}.closeAds{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5}.articlerelatepannel{padding:6px;margin-top:5px;margin-bottom:5px;background-color:#f7f7f7;border:solid 1px #069241}.articlerelate{padding:6px;display:list-item;list-style-type:square;margin-left:1.2em;border-bottom:dashed 1px #888}.articlerelate:last-child{border-bottom:0}div.articlerelate>a{color:#000;text-decoration:none;font-size:13px;font-weight:bold}div.articlerelate>a:hover{color:#f00;text-decoration:none;font-size:13px;font-w