 v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a Real Madrid</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, trung v\u1ec7 John Stones \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng sau khi b\u1ecb Pep Guardiola b\u1ecf r\u01a1i. T\u1eeb th\u00e1ng 1 \u0111\u1ebfn nay c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1994 ch\u01b0a \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn n\u00e0o \u1edf Premier League, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn anh ch\u00e1n n\u1ea3n v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chuyen nhuong Man City 2018 kien quyet khong ban cac ngoi sao hinh anh\" title=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Man City 2018 ki\u00ean quy\u1ebft kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n c\u00e1c ng\u00f4i sao h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/26/man-city-co-doi-loi-nhan-gui-den-real-madrid.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Real Madrid quan t\u00e2m Sterling v\u00e0 De Bruyne</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/nang-cap-hang-thu-real-bat-ngo-muon-co-bom-xit-cua-man-city-180-184991.html\" target=\"_blank\">Real quan t\u00e2m John Stones</span>, h\u1ecd s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng gi\u1ea3i c\u1ee9u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y. \u0110\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Bernabeu ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi ra 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh. HLV Zidane \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a Stones v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a anh r\u1eddi s\u00e2n Etihad.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i trung v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh, Real c\u00f2n quan t\u00e2m Kevin De Bruyne c\u1ee7a Man City. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 \u0111ang l\u00e0 nh\u1ea1c tr\u01b0\u1edfng trong l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a Man xanh, Los Blancos mu\u1ed1n chi 100 tri\u1ec7u euro cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nB\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh Leroy Sane v\u00e0 Raheem Sterling c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u01b0a v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm, Real nh\u1eafm nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y thay Gareth Bale, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Bernabeu v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 6 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Man City c\u00f3 c\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi cho Real Madrid</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Man City 2018 s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o cho Real Madrid, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 t\u1eeb ph\u00eda BL\u0110 Man xanh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Pep Guardiola phat bieu ve tran Man City vs Swansea\" title=\"Pep Guardiola ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Man City vs Swansea\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/23/huy-diet-swansea-pep-guardiola-noi-gi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Pep Guardiola kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n b\u00e1n c\u00e1c ng\u00f4i sao cho Real Madrid</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nT\u1edd Manchester Evening News kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Man City \u01b0u ti\u00ean gi\u1eef nh\u1eefng tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi ngh\u0129 \u0111\u1ebfn chuy\u1ec7n mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 m\u1edbi \u1edf H\u00e8 n\u00e0y. Theo \u0111\u00f3 Leroy\u00a0Sane, Kevin De Bruyne, Raheem Sterling v\u00e0 John Stones \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ec3 b\u00e1n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Etihad kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh d\u00f9 Real c\u00f3 chi nhi\u1ec1u ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u00e2u th\u00ec h\u1ecd c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ea3 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Trong s\u1ed1 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y De Bruyne v\u00e0 Sterling \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p c\u1ee7a John Stones, Pep kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u01b0a s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y v\u00ec anh kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ec3 tr\u1ea1ng t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t. V\u1ecb chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao c\u1ef1u sao Everton trong l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a Man xanh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTheo Mirror, chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Man City s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1edf H\u00e8 2018. BL\u0110 Man xanh s\u1ebd c\u1ea5p cho Pep Guardiola 200 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 mua s\u1eafm c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"1647","checkdouble":"185049"}]}